title: 12/27/21 DPS Hour 1 Jason McIntyre & Geoff Schwartz talk NFL Week 16
itunes:title: 12/27/21 DPS Hour 1 Jason McIntyre & Geoff Schwartz talk NFL Week 16
description:
Jason McIntyre and Geoff Schwartz, in for Dan Patrick, wrap up Week 16 in the NFL as the Kansas City Chiefs seem to have taken the crown of “Best Team in the NFL”! PFF’s Brad Spielberger stops by to talk some NFL football, and more!
